column5: Glanced the posts on the front page just now, and there was nothing about fishing?? - just pic questions, old posts, slow PC's - but no fishing??  So - here is goes -  Going out on Simcoe Saturday - going from 9'th line - all out there- give us a shout on your "cobra" radios - channel 1-1-1  Tite lines!!
Well come back Saturday or Sunday and you'll see lots of fishing posts  Joey
....It would seem your origional post was in the wrong forum and one of the Mods moved it here. Lots of fishing reports on this page and the ensuing pages.
You most likely don't have the same front page as everyone else. I just looked and it's 76% fishing.
Did you calculate that in your head Roy?  Joey
Spiel had it right...I noticed this thread on the "Help" section of the board...it's now in it's right home.
